00:34:56.362 --> 00:35:15.563
<v Leo> And that strength took you from obscure political agitator to Führer with near absolute power. In my era, we still see politicians employing massive rallies, albeit in different contexts. However, mass media coverage also scrutinizes them. Would that have impeded you if the press were truly free and global?

00:35:15.563 --> 00:35:51.362
