00:36:57.802 --> 00:37:12.722
<v Leo> And ironically, that choice dooms entire armies. In my era, we view that as catastrophic for Germany, yet you see it as essential to maintain your mystique. That's a hallmark of your approach, sacrificing practical realities for the appearance of invincibility.

00:37:12.722 --> 00:38:06.123
