00:38:06.123 --> 00:38:20.702
<v Leo> That is precisely why historians label your regime as driven by ideological fanaticism to the point of self-destruction and why you're seen as epitomizing evil, killing millions, including children, for no rational, strategic gain.

00:38:20.702 --> 00:38:38.862
<v Adolf Hitler> (speaks German) Modern moralizing ab-. In the Reich, we believed removing internal enemies was crucial. If we lost on the battlefield, it's because of other factors, not because we wasted time on the Jewish question. My personal convictions demanded no compromise.

00:38:38.862 --> 00:38:55.842
<v Leo> Understood. Let's shift briefly to how your name lingers. In comedic satire, you're occasionally mocked, films like The Great Dictator or modern skits. Some see this as diminishing your malevolence by turning you into a clownish figure. Thoughts on humor directed at you?

00:38:55.842 --> 00:39:20.103
<v Adolf Hitler> (speaks German) The idea. In my time, we censored mockery or jokes at my expense. If your future world parodies me, they do so to reduce fear, to transform me into a farce. Laughter can undermine tyranny's aura. I find it offensive, of course, but I'm not present in your era to quash it. So let them laugh if it soothes them.

00:39:20.103 --> 00:39:42.483
<v Leo> Yes. Satirists argue that ridiculing tyrants is a way to deflate their mystique. Another point, your personal finances. You grew wealthy through book royalties from Mein Kampf and avoided taxes. In modern times, we see some leaders abusing office for personal gain. You always claimed to serve Germany selflessly. Was that sincere?

00:39:42.483 --> 00:40:09.282
<v Adolf Hitler> My personal wealth was incidental. Royalties, gifts, these are trifles compared to the destiny of Deutschland. I had no interest in a lavish lifestyle. Yes, I accepted privileges, cars, estates, but these served my station. If modern leaders exploit power for purely material greed, that's more mundane than my vision. For me, it was about building an empire, not mere enrichment.

00:40:09.282 --> 00:40:30.630
<v Leo> Interesting. Let's talk about the allies in your time. The British Empire, the United States, the Soviet Union formed a coalition against you. In the future, you're recognized as the impetus that forced these nations to unite despite political differences.... even Stalin joined forces with Churchill and Roosevelt. Surprising, right?

00:40:30.630 --> 00:40:59.688
<v Adolf Hitler> Ja. I initially believed the Soviet-British divide was too great, but my aggression drove them together. That is the misfortune. I inadvertently created a powerful alliance. Britain alone might have eventually sought peace. The Soviet Union might have crumbled if we advanced swiftly. But with American industry backing them, it became formidable. Krieg can unify even natural adversaries if threatened by a larger menace, namely the Reich.

00:40:59.688 --> 00:41:16.610
<v Leo> Exactly. Now, can you reflect on how your propaganda demonized the Judeo-Bolshevik conspiracy, equating Jews with communism? In modern scholarship, that's considered a prime example of a Big Lie technique, just repeating a false narrative until people accept it. Is that how you see it?

00:41:16.610 --> 00:41:43.728
<v Adolf Hitler> I believed it fundamentally. I saw communism as a Jewish-led movement. That might be an oversimplification, but it resonated with the public. If repeating something ensures widespread conviction, so be it. Joseph Goebbels stressed the power of the Big Lie. The masses are more prone to believe a great falsehood repeated often than a small one. So, ja, we harnessed that tactic.

00:41:43.728 --> 00:42:06.349
<v Leo> And that's studied in modern media literacy courses to show how propaganda can manipulate entire societies. Another angle, a surprising number of modern conspiracy theories still tie global events to alleged secret Jewish cabals referencing your arguments. People label such beliefs as antisemitic conspiracies. Disturbing that these remain alive.

00:42:06.349 --> 00:42:29.429
<v Adolf Hitler> It suggests my central thesis about Jewish influence still appeals to certain minds. Even if the mainstream condemns it, conspiracies thrive in any environment that fosters suspicion. If a segment of the population feels disenfranchised, they search for scapegoats. Meine propaganda was tailored for that. I see no surprise in it persisting.

00:42:29.429 --> 00:42:46.449
<v Leo> All right, let's address the emotional toll. Millions died in your war, not only soldiers but also civilians bombed in their homes. Cities like Dresden and Hamburg were destroyed by Allied bombers. Do you hold any remorse about the suffering inflicted upon everyday Germans?

00:42:46.449 --> 00:43:08.989
<v Adolf Hitler> I lament that we lacked the means to protect them or retaliate more effectively, but Krieg spares no one. My focus was on securing final victory. Civilians suffer in all conflicts. I do not single out my own blame for that. The Allies likewise bombed recklessly. Such is total war. Compassion for them does not alter the reality of conflict.

00:43:08.989 --> 00:43:33.929
