00:43:33.929 --> 00:43:52.929
<v Adolf Hitler> Only that I acted with absolute conviction for Deutschland's supremacy and the eradication of what I saw as corrosive influences. If the world brands me as the greatest villain, it's because I failed. Had I succeeded, the narrative would be different. But that is the nature of history.

00:43:52.929 --> 00:44:11.548
<v Leo> And so we've reached the end of this dialogue. Your words reaffirm the necessity of guarding against fearmongers, hatemongers, and those who place ideology over human life. My era's people must remain vigilant, for the seeds of tyranny can sprout anywhere, often in crises fueled by resentment.

00:44:11.548 --> 00:44:23.268
<v Adolf Hitler> So, Syas, you come from a time that condemns me completely. I remained true to my beliefs, unwavering even in defeat. Return to your modern world and proclaim your warnings if you must.

